name: BURNA BOY KILOMETER BEAT BREAKDOWN PRODUCED BY CHOPSTIX

metadata.name: BURNA BOY 'KILOMETER' BEAT BREAKDOWN PRODUCED BY CHOPSTIX
metadata.description:
Here's the official beat breakdown to Burna Boy's "LAST LAST" soundtrack produced by Chopstix.

Chopstix is one of the most reputable music producer in Africa and has been instrumental to the development of Nigerian music and talent, far and wide. He's popularly known for his smash collaborations with Burna Boy, Ice Prince, Yung L, Major Lazer, Sean Paul, Giggs, Chip and recently executive produced a film driven EP for IRIE SESSIONS.
